Designed and implemented an Oozie workflow to find out:

  a) the 3 airlines with the highest and lowest probability, respectively, for being on schedule;
  b) the 3 airports with the longest and shortest average taxi time per flight (both in and out), respectively; and
  c) the most common reason for flight cancellations.

- src directory contains the FlightDataAnalysis.java file consisting of 3 mapreduce programs

- map-reduce directory contains job.properties & workflow.xml files

- map-reduce/lib/ contains the testoozie.jar file

- commands.txt consists of all the commands used to run the Hadoop/Oozie workflow

- output.txt contains the output of Oozie workflow execution

- Project Report in PDF format 
